# old timey sounding words that i think are cool and we should bring back

## forsooth

in truth, indeed. often used ironically.

> forsooth, my lady, it jiggle!

## antediluvian

before the biblical flood; hilarously old-fashioned

> As the man they called "Ho!" told his story of woe
> In an antediluvian tone.
the hunting of the snark, lewis carroll
